165
00:11:01,110 --> 00:11:04,910
You can't keep stomping on people's dreams all the time and get away with it.

166
00:11:09,920 --> 00:11:11,190
Whose gun was that?

167
00:11:11,330 --> 00:11:14,230
John'S. Always kept it at work.

168
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:16,810
So many crazies out there.

169
