571
00:35:35,110 --> 00:35:36,670
Just like his little girl.

572
00:35:37,060 --> 00:35:38,540
Your scarlet rose.

573
00:35:40,140 --> 00:35:42,020
I was so afraid to tell you.

574
00:35:43,080 --> 00:35:44,850
So you did it in a song.

575
00:35:44,960 --> 00:35:46,140
You listened to it?

576
00:35:47,300 --> 00:35:48,580
It's beautiful.

