00:36:17,720 --> 00:36:20,500
Lots of cigarettes and booze  and...

586
00:36:23,430 --> 00:36:24,830
lots of static.

587
00:36:26,300 --> 00:36:28,670
Dottie was right. It was...it was no place for a kid.

588
00:36:28,680 --> 00:36:30,550
I wouldn't have cared.

589
00:36:37,350 --> 00:36:41,300
How 'bout we take that trip to anywhere?

590
00:36:43,560 --> 00:36:45,450
Let me make up for lost time.

591
00:36:47,470 --> 00:36:49,090
What about your show?

592
00:36:49,100 --> 00:36:53,960
I told 'em I was going to take a little time off to spend with my family.

593
00:37:02,270 --> 00:37:03,630
We talked about leaving in a couple of weeks.

594
00:37:04,640 --> 00:37:08,100
He said I could sing backup with a band in california.

595
00:37:08,420 --> 00:37:11,610
