597
00:37:16,280 --> 00:37:17,740
I never told her.

598
00:37:18,260 --> 00:37:19,470
You sure?

599
00:37:20,160 --> 00:37:21,620
Might get her upset.

600
00:37:21,630 --> 00:37:24,810
That might even go talk to the hawk.

601
00:37:26,070 --> 00:37:27,550
Try to stop him.

602
00:37:30,140 --> 00:37:33,850
Everything my mom did was because she loved me.

603
00:37:38,790 --> 00:37:42,170
I understand you and hawk had a daughter?

