605
00:37:48,450 --> 00:37:53,090
Still. It's,uh...strange how you left that out.

606
00:37:53,440 --> 00:37:57,090
John was never much of a father. So,uh,it didn't matter.

607
00:37:59,080 --> 00:38:00,820
What about your own father?

608
00:38:02,910 --> 00:38:04,190
What does he have to do with this?

609
00:38:04,200 --> 00:38:08,370
Your mom died young,and your father raised you.

610
00:38:09,510 --> 00:38:11,130
The musician?

611
00:38:11,740 --> 00:38:15,760
If you can call playing at holiday inns along route 1 being a musician.

612
00:38:15,770 --> 00:38:18,920
Died on the road at age 43.

613
00:38:20,570 --> 00:38:21,550
Suicide.

