00:38:23,330 --> 00:38:27,450
I can see how jenny wanting to be a singer was upsetting.

615
00:38:28,580 --> 00:38:29,660
She wouldn't listen to me.

616
00:38:29,670 --> 00:38:32,940
She thought her passion was enough to give it a try.

617
00:38:32,950 --> 00:38:35,100
Passion is for fools.

618
00:38:35,830 --> 00:38:40,580
