00:39:46,440 --> 00:39:49,760
A daughter is someone you raise.

635
00:39:50,510 --> 00:39:52,690
Someone you take to girl scouts,

636
00:39:52,700 --> 00:39:55,750
someone you make dinner for every night,

637
00:39:55,760 --> 00:39:57,580
