641
00:40:05,000 --> 00:40:06,790
You abandoned us.

642
00:40:06,800 --> 00:40:09,080
You're a selfish son of a bitch,and you always will be.

643
00:40:09,090 --> 00:40:10,910
I'm not that man anymore.

